sources.description:
A Russian ex-Spetsnaz working as a mechanic in LA accepts a job freeing a kidnapped woman in Saint Petersburg, as the mob boss also killed his wife and son 7 years ago. The body count begins.
2005.  Stars: Dolph Lundgren, Ben Cross, Ivan Petrushinov
